{"tid":664018,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"大家買notebook睇咩？","createTime":"2018-05-13T18:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T03:18:39.000Z","uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"71249e5d08fde8227896c979f56cf4d4def4da64","tid":664018,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"1. CPU性能/RAM/高速儲存/高容量<br />\n2. GPU性能/打機<br />\n3. 高電量/高續航<br />\n4. 靚外觀 (邊框/有冇RGB/外型)<br />\n5. 靚mon (IPS/144hz/4k)<br />\n6. 低重量/細體積<br />\n7. 多IO位/種類 (HDMI/RJ45/USB頭數量)<br />\n8. 牌子/保養/售後<br />\n9. 可升級性 (可唔可以換SSD/加RAM)<br />\n10. Keyboard/Touchpad好唔好用<br />\n11. 高性價比/低價<br />\n<br />\n我主要睇薄邊框同IPS mon<br />\nCPU依家4c8t，做野黎講已經夠快<br />\nRAM要16GB，唔夠就要留位比人升級<br />\nIO最好有RJ45/HDMI，冇既話最少比個USB-A人<br />\n電既話，比我出街用成日，最好可以用尿袋經USB-C差<br />\n牌子/保養唔係特別臭就得，唔好比我網上見到人話成日壞<br />\nkeyboard/touchpad冇所謂<br />\n性價比方面，唔好比我同一個價錢+size買到spec更加好既機<br />\n一定要ssd，唔要hdd，送比我都會拆落黎。ssd可以sata或者nvme都得，256gb起跳<br />\nGPU唔需要<br />\n重量就1.2-1.8kg, 13-15吋，邊框要薄"},{"pid":"baedea3620e53a21272589b3f0dd51a7bd1ffd93","tid":664018,"uid":99941,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:41:20.000Z","msg":"申手黨"},{"pid":"ad4fc18dba55d280441b10e4a4be12b141e9f387","tid":664018,"uid":172648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:55:29.000Z","msg":"睇牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613e7383385b676a43966e760cfb273928266331","tid":664018,"uid":157223,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:07:23.000Z","msg":"睇下自己銀包先"},{"pid":"26edcea5cb68563e91ec34d594a031789d978cbd","tid":664018,"uid":164876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"613e7383385b676a43966e760cfb273928266331","tid":664018,"uid":157223,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:07:23.000Z","msg":"睇下自己銀包先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:08:21.000Z","msg":"So damn true"},{"pid":"029a8732ffa52107a43552cddb2067f46118ccb8","tid"